>
> We are looking for candidates with the following skillset:
>
> - Dev experience within a dynamic web environment - Python/Django, Ruby on
> Rails, or PHP
>
> - Experience and/or interest in SaaS design and implementation
>
> - Experience and/or interest in RESTful API design
>
> - Familiarity with ffmpeg, CDNs, and AWS Elastic Transcoder
>
> - Familiarity with video codecs and streaming protocols
>
> - Needless to say, we are looking for really dedicated and enthusiastic
> people
>
> Internship details:
>
> We are based out of Chennai and the internship will require the candidate
> to work for around two months with us (online or offline). The candidate
